{"tid":985981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秀茂坪2校巴相撞　至少15名幼稚園學童受傷","createTime":"2019-01-18T05:58:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T06:16:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"14ddde33c57260e20e48a34b266b5efca4acb0f8","tid":985981,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/photo/bkn-20190118132826682-0118_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190118135244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190118%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190118132826682-0118_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190118135244&h=2fe94d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n秀茂坪發生交通意外，今午(18日)1時36分，秀明道觀塘官立小學對開，發生兩輛校巴相撞意外，現場消息指，至少有15名幼稚園學童及1名保母受傷，需要送院治理。警方正展開調查。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/bkn-20190118132826682-0118_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190118%2Fbkn-20190118132826682-0118_00822_001.html&d=QL8Dn08IhbOMzyUdcig6xf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=be06be4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190118/bkn-20190118132826682-0118_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5139bbe70ba5aa82719324d1e7454cfe38bcfbe9","tid":985981,"uid":76341,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T05:59:36.000Z","msg":"而家搭校巴仲危險過搭巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b3930bd20cc29472f9b18f4ea6b7515b012ece","tid":985981,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:01:30.000Z","msg":"其實政府應該學補貼農兵咁補貼埋司機<br />\n畢竟交通安全對社會都好重要下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f574ed83f278492523d4820c11b92dbaf743d8","tid":985981,"uid":79077,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T06:02:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fb2d67ba59